attachments.text:
hi! we want to learn to make things better.

we expect that this feedback form will take about an hour to fill-in fully. we would like each of you to please spend some time and think through how you can make the course better for those that come after you.

tips:
-the survey is anonymous. if you want to identify yourself, no problem
-we want your honest input - be professional and polite, but clear and hold us to the same high standard that we held you during the 12 weeks.
-please do review the weekly challenges and other materials when providing answers

we will take your feedback seriously and use it to improve our training for future batches.
